
# ACTION REQUIRED: You must add your Firebase Admin SDK Service Account Key here.
# 1. Go to Firebase Console > Project Settings > Service accounts.
# 2. Click "Generate new private key". A JSON file will be downloaded.
# 3. Open the JSON file, copy the ENTIRE content.
# 4. Go to a base64 encoder website (e.g., base64encode.org) and paste the JSON to encode it.
# 5. Paste the resulting base64 string here. It will be a very long single line of text.
FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY_BASE64=""
